item.description:
Look up Dub music, like roots reggae with lots of echoes, percussion, loops, cuts and samples from the 70s. King tubby, scientist, lee Perry. I used to listen to stuff like this for hours at a time. It was 20+ years old then! I’d lean into this man, it’s different and I like it.
